member.name: douyhe
member.desc:
Composer

Hi, FNM server. I am Doyne, and I came here to look for help on my new mod.

Presenting FRIDAY NIGHT FUNKIN VS DOUYHE CORRUPTION: EXPANDED!

This mod will feature 7501 NEW WEEKS, featuring old and new characters, totalling up to 1859 SONGS! (Don’t worry, I’ll make those). We’re also adding a brand new original mechanic for each new week, which means there’s 800 MECHANICS in this one mod! That’s crazy, right? We’re also going to add a hub world, a mission system and 900+ ACHIEVEMENTS for you to collect, all on a brand new engine made specifically for the mod!

Of course, I will need a LOT of people to finish the mod. Unfortunately, I am a minor and cannot pay you guys, so this will all be for free. You will be paid with exposure on my channel with 98 subscribers, though.

We need the following people:

Artists ( 1 / 1000 ) – Seeing as this mod will have 800 weeks, we need artists for the backgrounds, character animations, and UI! It’ll need to be done in the FNF style, as I’m aiming to make this mod as accurate as possible.

Coders ( 1 / 1000 ) – Coding all of the features in will take a lot of people. You need to do this on your own game engine, as using existing engines isn’t too fancy and I don’t like it.

Musicians ( 1 / 1000 ) – Yes, I’m doing the music, but I’ll also need a bunch of people to do the vocals for the songs (I use a mobile app to do music). Also, 2400 songs is a lot, so assistance would be nice!

Voice Actors ( 1 / 100 ) – The original game has voice actors for the vocals, so we will too! You only need to voice all of the fully animated cutscenes and give the vocal artists samples.

DM me if you’re interested. Remember, this is all for free because I’m a minor
